{"title":"春雪飘飘","authors":["曹宇翔"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":4,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雪飘飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曹宇翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远近近只是这迷蒙的白啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天打扫最后的库存"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷扬扬，商量着飘落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小雪花顾盼生姿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"簪满家园门楣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又被春风摘下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节日硕大的“福”字多么照眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富足，安生，炊烟缭绕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座座村庄散落大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙角农具做着五谷飘香的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中打量古老节气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天地不朽，万物与谁为一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动颂歌深处，那是什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在阵阵闪光呀？仿佛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命根，源泉和真理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远近近只是这迷蒙的白啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切都沉浸在这美景中了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放寒假的村中小学生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文具盒里的尺子请借我一用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"量一量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这融融雪音，到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明媚春光和遍野禾浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有几米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡路新绿，隐约"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平原上的列车一声汽笛"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}